T}$ is non-stationary is\nbriefly discussed. As an application, we derive a Berry-Esseen bound for the\nM-estimators associated with $\\rho$-mixing Markov chains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Jan 2012 17:31:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-27"}
