etween TSu and total body length\nallows monitoring the growth of gilthead sea bream using low cost equipment\nlike single beam echosounders.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2012 12:11:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-24"}
