rocess seems to be suppressed in a similar way as\nexpected in the extension of the standard model by a light (<neV) pseudoscalar\n(axion-like) particle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2012 13:25:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2012 20:08:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
